hods made it possible to determine the environmental risks of the region, to create a basis for further research on the territory of the Tula region. The energy efficiency indicators of various types of "green" roofs, obtained as a result of thermal engineering calculations, as well as the identified accumulation capabilities, allowed us to draw conclusions about the prospects for the introduction of "green" technologies and the need for further research in the field of energy conservation and thermal inertia of enclosing structures of construction objects.
